						<h1>
															How can I cancel my hosting account?									</h1>
			
																
				
					<div style='font-size:12px; color:#aaa; margin-bottom:-10px; padding-top:5px;'>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Written by </span><a href='https://plus.google.com/102670474114655224886?rel=author'>Brad Markle</a></div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Views:</span> <span name='page_views' id='page_views'>57,455</span></div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;' title='Originally published: Oct 17, 2011'><span style='color:#606060;'>Published:</span> Apr 16, 2014</div>
							<div style='float:left; margin-right:20px;'><span style='color:#606060;'>Comments:</span> <a href='#comments'>57</a></div>
							<div style='clear:both;'></div>
						</div>
						</div>
		
	
		

	

								<p>We are sorry to hear that you want to cancel your hosting account!</p>

<p>We strive to offer the best tech support in the industry. If you're having any difficulties with your account, we are more than happy to help! Our Support Department is available 24/7 via phone or chat:</p>

<ul>
<li>Call us at   888-321-HOST (4678)  / 757-416-6575</li>
<li><a href="http://www.inmotionhosting.com/support/launch-chat/?rdid=2324923566971164486">Click here to start a live Chat session</a></li>
</ul>
 If you have any further questions, please feel free to <a href="/support/website/website-troubleshooting/how-to-get-great-technical-support">contact us at any time</a>.</p>

<p>Most of our plans include a 90 day money back guarantee.  This period of time should allow you to test additional programs available with your account if that is the issue. For example, if you're not sure if the <a href="/support/edu/premium-website-builder">Premium Website Builder</a> is going to meet your needs, you can <a href="/support/edu/wordpress">try using WordPress instead</a>.</p>

<h2>How to disable auto-renew</h2>

<p>Disabling auto renewals is the same process as a cancellation.  To do so, please contact our Support Department at any time and request that your account be set to expire.  Your account will then no longer be active after the time that has already been paid in advance.  Of course, if you decide in the future that you want to renew again, please contact Support so that they may renew your hosting account.</p>

<h2>Before you begin the cancellation process</h2>

<p>If you still intend to cancel the account, we understand. Please have the following information ready in order to make your cancellation a smooth process:</p>

<ul>
<li>Account Username</li>
<li>The last 4 digits of the credit card on file</li>
<li>Email address</li>
<li>Daytime phone number</li>
</ul>

<p>To cancel your account, or turn off auto-renewal please contact our Support and Billing Department at any time. We recommend calling us at <em><strong>888-321-4678 ext 2</strong> (US customers) or <strong>+1-757-416-6575 ext 2</strong> (international customers)</em> as the fastest method, followed by <a class="no-margin chat" onclick="launchBoldChat();return false;" rel='nofollow'>chat</a>, and then <a href="/support/website/website-troubleshooting/how-to-get-great-technical-support#submit-ticket">creating a ticket</a> if necessary.</p> 
	
